                "name": "Page_GearEquipment",
                "fieldName": "gearequipment",
                "group": "Page",
                "descriptions": ["This section is divided into two categories, Equipment and Gear.", "Equipment are items that must be equipped to give any kind of benefit. These items must be equipped into Equipment slots in order to be used during a conflict. You always have a base of 4 Consumable slots but can gain more by spending Perk Points or by wearing specific types of equipment.", "Equipment is divided into three types, Weapons, Apparel, and Tools. Weapons generally provide new techniques for you to use in combat and provide keywords to allow the use of weapon styles. Tools also grant keywords and techniques but have a support theme. Apparel will usually offer stat bonuses and always have a slot associated with them. You can only equip one item of each Apparel type.", "Gear are items that do not need to be equipped. These will usually be used for crafting or provide other unique benefits."],
