                "fieldName": "highqualitymeals",
                "group": "System",
                "descriptions": ["A high quality meal is made and served at ideal temperatures, is well prepared, and nutritious. These meals always need to be consumed as soon as they are finished being prepared, otherwise they lose the high quality trait.", "A character that consumes a high quality meal always gains their Savor Boon. Some recipes and preparations from certain character abilities may add additional benefits to consuming a high quality meal."],
