                "name": "Title_ValidTargets",
                "fieldName": "validtargets",
                "group": "Title",
                "descriptions": ["The following are valid targets for attacks and effects:", "• other characters;\n• objects that aren’t held or worn;\n• spaces in the environment or on the ground.", "To attack or take an action against a target, by default the target must be within range and within the attacker’s line of sight. Unless otherwise specified, characters can’t target themselves."],
